Happy 37th birthday to 3x All-Star & 2007 Rookie of the Year, Brandon Roy!

B-Roy is one of the greatest “what-if” players of all-time! 💔💯

node.text:
Kevin Durant was getting love from his fellow Olympics at this morning’s opening ceremony! 🇺🇸

Durant was getting asked to take photos with multiple Olympians & one said, “you’re so nice, you take pictures with everybody!” 

Durant responded with: “They try to paint me as a villain but I’m a nice person at the end of the day.” 💯

BREAKING: LeBron James is the first NBA player to earn $1 Billion during his playing career. 

$330 Million in playing salary 
$700 Million in endorsements 

LeBron is also the 5th athlete to do it as an active player, joining Tiger Woods, Floyd Mayweather, Cristiano Ronaldo, Lionel Messi. 

Legendary stuff ‼️👑
